creator: Toyota Motor North America, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
TSCS. Toyota Shipping Confirmation System focuses on improving two areas of the supply chain

TSCS. Toyota Shipping Confirmation System focuses on improving two areas of the supply chain
1. Supplier Packing: Identify contents of each skid as order is filled (Box to Skid linkage)
2. Supplier Shipping: Scan each skid on to Toyota truck at supplier
--> 3 platforms are available for Supplier to capture and communicate skid and shipment data to Toyota
Toyota Shipping Confirmation Mobile
Utilize any iOS or Android device that can connect to mobile data network
Designed for suppliers who do not have existing scanning processes on shipping dock
Can be used by any supplier
descriptionShort: App for Suppliers who do not have existing scanning processes on shipping dock

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Fixed setting 'Use Old Scan Mode' not saving between app sessions.
Fixed rare case of incorrectly getting 'Duplicate Order' errors on Skid Shipment Load when submitting a load with unplanned Skids.
